## Environment variables

All variables are documented in `.env.example`. Load order:
- Local dev: `.env` file (loaded automatically by the framework)
- Production: set on your hosting platform (see README.md)

{{#hasNeon}}
**`DATABASE_URL`** — Neon PostgreSQL connection string. Must include `?sslmode=require`.
{{/hasNeon}}
{{#hasClerk}}
**`NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY`** / **`CLERK_SECRET_KEY`** — from Clerk dashboard.
{{/hasClerk}}
{{#hasStripe}}
**`STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET`** — different for local dev (from Stripe CLI) vs production (from Stripe dashboard).
{{/hasStripe}}
{{#hasLlmApi}}
**`ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`** — from [console.anthropic.com](https://console.anthropic.com).
{{/hasLlmApi}}

